haywood.bcs345.hwk.vet.business

Class Pet

  • java.lang.Object
    • haywood.bcs345.hwk.vet.business.Pet

  • public class Pet
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains member variables and methods for the Pet class. If an instance in Main is called will create a Pet object. Accepts parameters to set Pet name and price, read an input file containing pet data, write member variables to an output file. Can create a JSON formatted string if method is called.
    Since:
    9/25/2018
    Version:

    Author:
    Jeffrey Haywood
